{"lemma":"رَتْقِ","slug":"رَتْقِ","root":"ر.ت.ق","root_slug":"ر-ت-ق","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ت-ق","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رَتْق","root":"رتق","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n14694","n14696","n14697"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%AA%D9%92%D9%82%D9%90"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n14694","headword_ar":"رَتَقَ","root":"rtq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, Msb) and"},{"kind":"text","text":", (L,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratoqN","text_ar":"رَتْقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, L, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He closed up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, Msb, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repaired,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, TA,) a rent: (S, M, Msb, TA:) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he sewed up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"together:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ritaAqN","text_ar":"رِتَاقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~atoqu","text_ar":"الرَّتْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfatoqu","text_ar":"الفَتْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,] one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rataqa fatoqahumo","text_ar":"رَتَقَ فَتْقَهُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning (tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He closed up the breach that was between them; he reconciled them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he reformed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amended, the circumstances subsisting between them."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratiqato","text_ar":"رَتِقَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (IKoot, Msb, TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rataqN","text_ar":"رَتَقٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, Msb, TA,) in the K, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rataqapN","text_ar":"رَتَقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"She was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, such as is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratoqaA='","text_ar":"رَتْقَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (IKoot, S, Mgh, Msb, K;) said of a woman, (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) or of a girl, and also of a camel. (IKoot, Msb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","L","Msb","M","K","TA","IKoot","Mgh"]},{"entry_id":"n14696","headword_ar":"رَتْقٌ","root":"rtq","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marotuwqN","text_ar":"مَرْتُوقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marotuwqapN","text_ar":"مَرْتُوقَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", &c., being originally an inf. n.; i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Closed up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"repaired;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a rent; and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rataqN","text_ar":"رَتَقٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kaAnataA","text_ar":"كَانَتَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratoqFA fafataqonaAhumaA","text_ar":"رَتْقًا فَفَتَقْنَاهُمَا"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the Kur [xxi. 31, lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They"},{"kind":"text","text":"(the heavens and the earth)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"were closed up, and we rent them"},{"kind":"text","text":"], is from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~atoqu","text_ar":"الرَّتْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as the contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alfatoqu","text_ar":"الفَتْقُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S:) accord. to Ibn-'Arafeh, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they were closed up, without any interstice, and we rent them by the rain and by the plants:"},{"kind":"text","text":"accord. to Az, it means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they were a heaven closed up and an earth closed up, and we rent them into seven heavens and seven earths:"},{"kind":"text","text":"Lth says that the heavens were closed up, no rain descending from them; and the earth was closed up, without any fissure therein; until God rent them by the rain and the plants: Zj says that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratoqFA","text_ar":"رَتْقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*awaAtaYo ratoqK","text_ar":"ذَوَاتَىْ رَتْقٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and he says that the heaven and the earth were united, and God rent them by the air, which He placed between them: (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ftq","text_ar":"فتق"},{"kind":"text","text":":) some read ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rataqFA","text_ar":"رَتَقًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayoy^FA rataqFA","text_ar":"شَيْيًا رَتَقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"marotuwqFA","text_ar":"مَرْتُوقًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Bd.)"}],"source_refs":["S","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n14697","headword_ar":"رَتَقٌ","root":"rtq","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph, in two places.       -A2-  It is [also] pl. [or rather coll. gen. n.] of ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rataqapN","text_ar":"رَتَقَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", syn., accord. to the copies of the K, with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rutobapN","text_ar":"رُتْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", but correctly with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ratabapN","text_ar":"رَتَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"space between"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"any two of"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the fingers:"},{"kind":"text","text":"mentioned [in the JK, where I find the correct reading, and] by Ibn-'Abbád. (TA.)"}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}